  <bioghist id="aspace_a1cdfd5d594705a2e82f31a31aef6b67">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Mary K. Bloetjes received a Ph.D. from Cornell University in 1953. She served as head of the Department of Institution Management in the College of Home Economics at Cornell from 1955 to 1969 and a a professor in the Department of Human Nutrition and Food in the College of Human Ecology from 1969 until her retirement in 1970.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_f19600bc21cdf4403f1f21c152f0a742">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Files concerning her retirement and role as an professor emeritus.</p>  </scopecontent>
